  <data key="d1">7.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Grace Period is the length of time after the premium is due and unpaid during which the policy remains in effect. If the full premium is paid during the grace period, the premium is considered to have been paid on time.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1ef4e957d14ec936b76e66af1fb9cf45</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Every action or proceeding against an insurer for the recovery of insurance money payable under the contract is absolutely barred unless commenced within the time set out in the Insurance Act (for actions or proceedings governed by the laws of Alberta and British Columbia), the Insurance Act (for actions or proceedings governed by the laws of Manitoba), the Limitations Act, 2002 (for actions or proceedings governed by the laws of Ontario), or other applicable legislation.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;As long as your premiums are paid when due, your TD 20-Year Term Life insurance will renew automatically for successive 20-year terms, with no medical examination required, providing continuous coverage until your 80th birthday. Premiums are fixed for each 20-year term and are guaranteed not to increase until each renewal date, regardless of your age or changes in your health.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Lapse refers to the termination of this policy because the premium was not paid within the grace period.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1ef4e957d14ec936b76e66af1fb9cf45</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;For those actions or proceedings governed by the laws of Quebec, the prescriptive period is set out in the Civil Code of Quebec.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Lapse Date refers to the date the policy lapses.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1ef4e957d14ec936b76e66af1fb9cf45</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Applicable Laws Your insurance will be governed by the laws of the province where you were resident when you initially applied for insurance under this policy, without reference to that province's rules about conflicts of laws.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Coverage can be converted from term life insurance to permanent life insurance at any time up to and including the policy anniversary nearest the insured's 69th birthday - again, with no medical examination required.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Insured person is the person whose life is insured under this policy.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1ef4e957d14ec936b76e66af1fb9cf45</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;English Language It is the express wish of the parties that this policy and all related documents, including notices and other communications, be drawn up in the English language only.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;This convenient and straightforward coverage is also available to your spouse, partner or other family members. Applying is as simple as visiting www.tdinsurance.com or calling the number below.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Policy means this document which provides evidence of your insurance.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">18.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1ef4e957d14ec936b76e66af1fb9cf45&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f6c86811679fb620e3f93424ae4b0a1</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;This section is applicable if you selected the Waiver of Premiums Benefit when you applied for TD 20-Year Term Life Insurance.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;You have a 30 day review period from your effective date to review your policy. During that time, you will be insured as outlined in the policy. If you're not completely satisfied and wish to cancel coverage, simply contact us within the 30 day period. Any premium charged to your account will be promptly refunded in full.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;In this booklet, we have provided answers to some frequently asked questions about term life insurance. If you still have questions, call toll-free 1-888-788-0839, Monday to Friday, 8 a.m. to 10 p.m. (ET) and Saturday 10 a.m. to 6 p.m., (ET), to speak to a TD Insurance representative.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Policy Owner is the person or party who owns this individual insurance policy. The policy owner is not necessarily the person whose life is insured.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">17.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1ef4e957d14ec936b76e66af1fb9cf45&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f6c86811679fb620e3f93424ae4b0a1</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;If while this policy is in effect, and before the insured person's 65th birthday, the insured person becomes totally disabled, as defined below, and remains totally disabled for a continuous period of six months, we will:&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Again, thank you for choosing TD Insurance. We appreciate your business and look forward to serving you and your family.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">6.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Reinstatement is&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">5.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1ef4e957d14ec936b76e66af1fb9cf45</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Automatically change the policy premium payment frequency to monthly, if the payment frequency is other than monthly, beginning with the date we agree to waive premiums. If after the end of the period of total disability, you wish to pay premiums other than monthly then you must notify us.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Underwritten by TD Life Insurance Company (referred to as 'the insurer' and 'we', 'us' and 'our' in this policy).&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">7.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;May choose to add a Waiver of Premium Benefit to the policy. This benefit must be added at the same time that you purchase TD 20-Year Term Life insurance.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-11d4c3dcf75b46d67d20b99fae497d13</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Waive the payment of monthly premiums from the date the insured person becomes totally disabled and for as long as the total disability continues, up to the insured person's 80th birthday.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;This Insurance Policy # 123 456 789 is issued to:&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">6.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bcfa08654ec1fe76b2e144274924604f</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;It can ensure that your coverage remains in place should you become disabled and cannot return to work, and may have problems paying for the policy.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-11d4c3dcf75b46d67d20b99fae497d13</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;'Total disability' or 'totally disabled' shall mean that the insured person, as a result of bodily injury or disease, is wholly prevented during the first two years after the injury or the onset of the disease from performing the substantial duties of their own occupation; after the first two years the insured person must be prevented by the injury or disease, from engaging in any gainful occupation for which they are or may reasonably become qualified by training, education or experience.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;When you think about it, it ensures your coverage can stay in force when you need it most.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">7.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-11d4c3dcf75b46d67d20b99fae497d13</data>
</node>
<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;If you exercise the conversion option in this policy while the insured person is totally disabled, we will not waive premiums for the converted insurance policy.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">8.0</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3176395bb041cd38db29d25c821dd001</data>
</node>
