<node id="&quot;TD LIFE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"TD Life Insurance Company, the insurer responsible for administering the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life can be informed to stop direct marketing contact."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life cannot guarantee the legal validity of beneficiary changes."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life collects information from interactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life is an organization that provides insurance and requires written approval for coverage to take effect."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life is authorized to receive health information from various sources."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life is authorized to receive information for claims purposes."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life is the organization that receives the request and processes changes to beneficiary designations."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life may report personal health information to MIB."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life offers products and services, but insurance purchase is not mandatory."&lt;SEP&gt;"TD Life requires submission of the application and supplementary forms."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurer that records and processes beneficiary changes."</data>
